## Compatibility
Editions:
- All Delphi Editions (Community, Professional, Enterprise and Architect)
- Lazarus Win32/Win64

Delphi Version:
- Delphi Seattle (10.0)
- Delphi Berlin (10.1)
- Delphi Tokyo (10.2)
- Delphi Rio (10.3)
- Delphi Sydney (10.4)
- Delphi Alexandria (11.3)
- Delphi Athens (12.0)
- Delphi Athens (13.0)

Lazarus Version (Windows Only):
- Lazarus 3.4
- Lazarus 3.6
- Lazarus 3.8
- Lazarus 4.0
- Lazarus 4.2
- Lazarus 4.4


